  BoomSound: {fileID: 474492951}
  Music: {fileID: 878360987}
  Ambient: {fileID: 469791911}
  Texts:
  - There was a beautiful planet, a planet where resourses were plentiful and people
    well fed...
  - But one day everything changed...
  - 'Humanity has lost all of it''s energy sources... '
  - There was no wind anymore
  - The oceans have stopped moving
  - The sun was too weak to produce solar energy
  - Everyday cities were dying one after another
  - The earth was in danger of complete destruction
  - Untill someone invented...
  - The chair
  _text: {fileID: 1888744437}
